workout:
row 250 meters, 10 burpees, 5 clean and jerks. Rest 2 minutes. 4 rounds. Row
                      and burpees should be all-out sprint. Clean and jerks heavy enoug to NOT be touch and go.
comments:
Last two rounds Anthony convinced us to really really sprint: my third round row
                      was 55.4 seconds (probably a record for me :), and I was wiped after it. No back problems
